I Love Money S01E05 DSR XviD-SYS(www.scenepirates.com)


Cry Me a River
Someone had some fat editing fingers. Missing minute at the end.



Coming off the heels of the previous elimination, a massive shift of power within the alliances takes place. The house is shaken up as secret deals are made and certain individuals become targets for elimination. At the challenge, the teams are forced to shed tears if they want to guarantee themselves immunity Things get hairy in the final hours, as deals that were made come close to falling apart, and one individual who was safe is now in potential jeopardy
